[Student "S"]
{Partner's 2NT bid requests that you bid 3\C, so you do.

He next says 3NT.  

Partner's bidding shows a hand with which he would have bid 3NT without the overcall. Furthermore, he promises a \H stopper. He expects you to pass, so you do.}

